--- steps
- init project
npm create vite@latest app_230316_wiki
- install pug
npm install -D pug pug-plain-loader --save-dev
- install sass
npm i sass --save-dev
npm i sass-loader@10 --save-dev
- import global sass in App.vue
- install typescript support for pugjs
npm install -D @volar/vue-language-plugin-pug
- add this into tsconfig.json
"vueCompilerOptions": {
  "plugins": ["@volar/vue-language-plugin-pug"]
}
- install vueRouter 4
npm install vue-router@4
- install axios
npm i axios
- use json-server to fake API
- install pinia
npm install pinia
- install country-list-json
npm i country-list-json
- install vue notification
npm i @kyvg/vue3-notification



